one who confesses his sins, O Allah, indeed the followers of truth cannot swallow their saliva down their neck (due to immense sorrow), and the truthful are captured in narrowness and restriction, and O Allah, You are gracious and kind towards Your slaves and devotees, and are worthy of fulfilling their request and hastening in their relief.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ مَنَاۗئِحُكَ مُتَتَابِعَۃٌ، وَاَیَادِیْكَ مُتَوَالِیَۃٌ، وَنِعَمُكَ سَابِغَۃٌ، وَشُكْرُنَا قَصِیْرٌ، وَحَمْدُنَا یَسِیْرٌ، وَاَنْتَ بِالتَّعَطُّفِ عَلٰی مَنِ اعْتَرَفَ جَدِیْرٌ۔ اَللّٰھُمَّ وَقَدْ غُصَّ اَهْلُ الْحَقِّ بِالرِّیْقِ، وَارْتَبَكَ اَهْلُ الصِّدْقِ فِی الْمَضِیْقِ، وَاَنْتَ اللّٰھُمَّ بِعِبَادِكَ وَذُوِی الرَّغْبَۃِ اِلَیْكَ شَفِیْقٌ، وَبِاِجَابَۃِ دُعَائِهِمْ وَتَعْجِیْلِ الْفَرَجِ عَنْهُمْ حَقِیْقٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016450, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, send peace upon Mohammad and his holy progeny (peace be upon them), and assist us immediately with Your help such that it is not followed by any humiliation and disgrace, and make us victorious such that no bad can make us suffer, and send such relief from Your lofty position that Your friend and devotee shall live in peace, but Your enemies shall be defeated, Your signs and impressions shall be established, Your commands shall become apparent, and those benefits that You had promised shall be availed. O Allah, show haste in showering mercy upon us, and immediately avenge and punish Your enemies with Your rage and wrath. O Allah, help us and hear our cries, and lift Your punishment and wrath from Us, and send them upon the transgressors.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ، وَبَادِرْنَا مِنْكَ بِالْعَوْنِ الَّذِیْ لَا خِذْلَانَ بَعْدَهٗ، وَالنَّصْرِ الَّذِیْ لَا بَاطِلَ یَتَكَاَّدُهٗ، وَاَتِحْ لَنَا مِنْ لَدُنْكَ مُتَاحًا فَیَّاحًا یَامَنُ فِیْۃِ وَ وَلِیُّكَ، وَیَخِیْبُ فِیْهِ عَدُوُّكَ، وَیُقَامُ فِیْهِ مَعَالِمُكَ، وَیَظْهَرُ فِیْهِ اَوَامِرُكَ، وَتَنْكَفٌّ فِیْهِ عَوَادِیْ عِدَاتِكَ۔ اَللّٰھُمَّ بَادِرْنَا مِنْكَ بِدَارَ الرَّحْمَۃِ، وَبَادِرْ اَعْدَائِكَ مِنْۢ بَاسِكَ بَدَارَ النَّقِمَۃِ۔ اَللّٰھُمَّ اَعِنَّ وَاَغِثْنَا، وَارْفَعْ نَقِمَتَلَ عَنَّا، وَاَحِلَّهَا بِالْقَوْمِ الظَّالِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14"